Implemented the Model Registry service with a "ModelRegistry" ORM model storing all required fields plus "mlflow_run_id" and "model_uri" for MLflow integration, including automatic champion promotion logic that marks the best-performing model based on ROC-AUC. Built the model artifact storage layer that serializes and uploads the trained model, evaluation metrics, and preprocessor to versioned MinIO paths. Created the "POST /train" endpoint that orchestrates the full training pipeline across the team's modules. Also updated "config.py", "main.py", "docker-compose.yml", "requirements.txt", and ".env.example" to support the new training service and MLflow tracking infrastructure.
